{"about_the_game":"Astrodle is an <strong><u>incremental space shooter</u></strong> that is all about collecting the essences of the Zodiac in a quest to become an immortal space god. <strong><u>Shoot</u></strong>, <strong><u>collect</u></strong>, <strong><u>upgrade</u></strong>, repeat, become a god. Sounds easy enough, right?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Shoot and Collect Essences</h2>Your spaceship comes equipped with lasers and that\u2019s too bad for the <strong><u>Blobs</u></strong>. Destroy as many as you can to collect <strong><u>Essences</u></strong> and make progress on your quest.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853130/extras/steam_page_01.gif?t=1718804789\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Upgrade your Ship</h2>Your lasers are awesome but you can make them better. Spend your essences on <strong><u>Upgrades</u></strong> and take your fire power to the next level.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853130/extras/steam_page_03.gif?t=1718804789\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Revel in the Numbers</h2>Now it\u2019s time to take a step back and <strong><u>admire the chaos</u></strong> you have unleashed on the blobs. All these numbers everywhere, isn\u2019t that perfect?<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853130/extras/steam_page_09.gif?t=1718804789\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Complete the story</h2>Space is vast but you are not alone. <strong><u>Sagittarius</u></strong>, <strong><u>Aquarius</u></strong> and <strong><u>Taurus</u></strong> are here to guide you through your quest to become a god. It's been a very long time since they have encountered a human but that's not a problem\u2026 right?<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853130/extras/steam_page_05.gif?t=1718804789\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Beat the game</h2>Don't you hate when you can't tell if you have finished an idle game or not? Both game modes of Astrodle have an end that can be reached in just a day when played actively. Ideal for playing lazily <strong><u>over the weekend</u></strong>.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Automation","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2853130/5ffdbc2904f84ed8c1d5123d82e25d5cec2c244d.jpg"},{"name":"Really cool space arrows","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2853130/c1ae9a32094c571e5f59524887662e649960b073.jpg"},{"name":"Something's wrong","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2853130/c83db1f1d8d9045fa3a6e610091c44ac0cef371f.jpg"},{"name":"A job well done","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2853130/f16ea38cc2fc916ff0256c9e35885641d38a791b.jpg"},{"name":"Mere mortal","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2853130/d3c4f3141f0af7f788247db27a2b2870250a1889.jpg"},{"name":"Personality check","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2853130/71ea3e0321de3a197be06b96577bacdb3008db7a.jpg"},{"name":"The answer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2853130/9741a36a20e02871b30f1dc84fb328f3370b9705.jpg"},{"name":"Let it flow","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2853130/e006cdb13e9187b4851b67bcbada0d7b76a61972.jpg"},{"name":"God as new","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2853130/04240683ea62f5ec71125849d2d6a06ccfabe960.jpg"},{"name":"Divine intervention","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2853130/57cbf3ecd993884014b8061ec6fe3a7b5cca05a5.jpg"}],"total":15},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853130/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1718804789","background_raw":"https://share